In order to carry on this mission, the Business Analyst needs to have a deep knowledge of the process of transforming needs into formal requirements and specifications of software applications, and will be the reference point for all matters related to the requirements and features of the product. Acting as the client of the development projects the product owner will direct the direction that Scytl products will take.</p>
